		   ITS_MESSAGETYPE_INTERNALADDQE &amp; Tab &amp; ITS_MESSAGETYPE_INTERNALDELQE &amp; Tab &amp; ITS_MESSAGETYPE_LOGOFF &amp; Tab &amp; ITS_MESSAGETYPE_LOGON &amp; Tab &amp; 
