		   ITS_MESSAGETYPE_REFRESHMACH &amp; Tab &amp; ITS_MESSAGETYPE_REJECT &amp; Tab &amp; ITS_MESSAGETYPE_RESETINTFACE &amp; Tab &amp; ITS_MESSAGETYPE_RESETMACH &amp; Tab &amp;
